{"tid":919220,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[殺手食評］- 冇得揀既 steak house","createTime":"2018-11-28T01:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T12:45:12.000Z","uid":221748,"like":5,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6dd916016a609364b5273615d07804e2f46e7045","tid":919220,"uid":221748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:30:37.000Z","msg":"🇭🇰#香港捐窿捐罅記<br />\n一間身處係中環黃金地帶既法式牛扒屋 冇menu 全間店只賣一個套餐 就係沙拉加牛扒 而且有5個人以上先可以book位 但都日日爆滿 睇下佢有幾爸閉先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n-<br />\n首先比一比背景資料先 佢賣既牛扒🐮全部都係usda prime. 咁usda 係美國一個比食品評級既組織 而牛扒係佢既其中一樣 通常可以切成牛扒比人食既等級得三個 choice , select , prime. Prime係最高級亦都係最罕見 佔全美總牛🐮數量既2% 油花肉質都係全美最top<br />\n-<br />\n環境方面 暗暗地 幾過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾浪漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾合適於情侶拍拖既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食物方面 餐包就少少熱 合桃沙律正正常常 冇乜驚喜 清清新新咁 算合格🙂 沙律之後就係牛扒啦 係10oz 既肉眼 牛味相當重 果然係美國牛 配上佢既法式蛋黃醬(Bearnaise) 味道一流 除此之外仲有任食薯條 用左牛油炸 所以好脆好香<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kCajVcD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCajVcD.png&h=963e9cc5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DqQG8xH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDqQG8xH.png&h=85de017b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後如果大家未飽仲可以點甜品 食左個Paris Brest 係佢地既signature dish 榛子味好食 少少甜 好正 好好味<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c8BK6jr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc8BK6jr.png&h=ee01f01a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KVeTZEw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKVeTZEw.png&h=6bfde588&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e4ZMAcV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe4ZMAcV.png&h=abd21700&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-<br />\n🎈中環蘇豪卑利街48號地下<br />\n-<br />\n平均傷害：$400<br />\n好味值：7.5/10<br />\n<br />\nInstagram :<a href=\"https://instagram.com/foodkiller_dk?utm_source=ig_profile_share&amp;igshid=16yo06jn1vb5c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Ffoodkiller_dk%3Futm_source%3Dig_profile_share%26igshid%3D16yo06jn1vb5c&d=E1T%2B3%2Fwi7mooJkZ6DPK9TW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=49bd311f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/foodkiller_dk?utm_source=ig_profile_share&amp;igshid=16yo06jn1vb5c</a>"},{"pid":"4a509b68cc76d26f52fff844972274c15d27548e","tid":919220,"uid":41546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:59:01.000Z","msg":"垃圾都吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你都係慳d咪再出食評啦<br />\nd扒overcook 肉汁又流失哂 <br />\n得d港女先會排隊食"},{"pid":"b38957fbb1eccb664ac64ea85b90e15b9054a352","tid":919220,"uid":221748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4a509b68cc76d26f52fff844972274c15d27548e","tid":919220,"uid":41546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:59:01.000Z","msg":"垃圾都吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你都係慳d咪再出食評啦<br />\nd扒overcook 肉汁又流失哂 <br />\n得d港女先會排隊食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:08:30.000Z","msg":"我食過三次都冇overtook <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n係咪你唔識睇"},{"pid":"d7c36121ceb554c865391fc4f38013654a386441","tid":919220,"uid":221748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b38957fbb1eccb664ac64ea85b90e15b9054a352","tid":919220,"uid":221748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4a509b68cc76d26f52fff844972274c15d27548e","tid":919220,"uid":41546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:59:01.000Z","msg":"垃圾都吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你都係慳d咪再出食評啦<br />\nd扒overcook 肉汁又流失哂 <br />\n得d港女先會排隊食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:08:30.000Z","msg":"我食過三次都冇overtook <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n係咪你唔識睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":